Interface MapExtractor

All Superinterfaces:
BeanExtractor<Map<String,Object>>, Iterable<Map<String,Object>>
public sealed interface MapExtractor extends BeanExtractor<Map<String,Object>>

Converts the rows in a JDBC ResultSet into Map<String, Object> pseudo-objects. Instances are obtained via MapExtractorFactory.getExtractor().

Ayco Holleman
